      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This car is the perfect canvas for your next restoration masterpiece. While it\u2019s currently in poor condition and needs a significant amount of TLC to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic opportunity to build a vehicle exactly how you want it. Grab this budget-friendly project today and bring some new life to a classic frame!",
