    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, original luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating applied last year; there are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Every panel gap is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, still retaining that new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the dash is completely free of sun damage or rattles. All electronic components, from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key and ready for any distance. It comes with a complete, documented service history from the local dealership, including a recent major service that replaced all fluids and filters. The engine bay is detailed and dry, with no leaks or corrosion. The original alloy wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in a fresh set of high-performance tires with less than 500 miles on them. This is an uncompromising example for a buyer who demands the absolute best. Includes two keys, original owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 45900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
